288 struct EstimationControl
289 {
290  struct EnableFlags : Bitfield<EnableFlags>
291  {
292  typedef uint16_t Type;
293  enum _enumType : uint16_t
294  {
295  NONE = 0x0000,
296  GYRO_BIAS = 0x0001,
297  ACCEL_BIAS = 0x0002,
298  GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0004,
299  ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR = 0x0008,
300  ANTENNA_OFFSET = 0x0010,
301  AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON = 0x0020,
302  AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON = 0x0040,
303  ALL = 0x007F,
304  };
305  uint16_t value = NONE;
306 
307  EnableFlags() : value(NONE) {}
308  EnableFlags(int val) : value((uint16_t)val) {}
309  operator uint16_t() const { return value; }
310  EnableFlags& operator=(uint16_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
311  EnableFlags& operator=(int val) { value = uint16_t(val); return *this; }
312  EnableFlags& operator|=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
313  EnableFlags& operator&=(uint16_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
314 
315  bool gyroBias() const { return (value & GYRO_BIAS) > 0; }
316  void gyroBias(bool val) { value &= ~GYRO_BIAS; if(val) value |= GYRO_BIAS; }
317  bool accelBias() const { return (value & ACCEL_BIAS) > 0; }
318  void accelBias(bool val) { value &= ~ACCEL_BIAS; if(val) value |= ACCEL_BIAS; }
319  bool gyroScaleFactor() const { return (value & GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
320  void gyroScaleFactor(bool val) { value &= ~GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; if(val) value |= GYRO_SCALE_FACTOR; }
321  bool accelScaleFactor() const { return (value & ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR) > 0; }
322  void accelScaleFactor(bool val) { value &= ~ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; if(val) value |= ACCEL_SCALE_FACTOR; }
323  bool antennaOffset() const { return (value & ANTENNA_OFFSET) > 0; }
324  void antennaOffset(bool val) { value &= ~ANTENNA_OFFSET; if(val) value |= ANTENNA_OFFSET; }
325  bool autoMagHardIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON) > 0; }
326  void autoMagHardIron(bool val) { value &= ~AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_HARD_IRON; }
327  bool autoMagSoftIron() const { return (value & AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON) > 0; }
328  void autoMagSoftIron(bool val) { value &= ~AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; if(val) value |= AUTO_MAG_SOFT_IRON; }
329  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
330  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
331  };
333  FunctionSelector function = static_cast<FunctionSelector>(0);
334  EnableFlags enable;
335 
337  static constexpr const uint8_t DESCRIPTOR_SET = ::mip::commands_filter::DESCRIPTOR_SET;
338  static constexpr const uint8_t FIELD_DESCRIPTOR = ::mip::commands_filter::CMD_ESTIMATION_CONTROL_FLAGS;
339  static constexpr const CompositeDescriptor DESCRIPTOR = {DESCRIPTOR_SET, FIELD_DESCRIPTOR};
340  static constexpr const char* NAME = "EstimationControl";
341  static constexpr const char* DOC_NAME = "Estimation Control Flags";
342  static constexpr const bool HAS_FUNCTION_SELECTOR = true;
343 
344  auto asTuple() const
345  {
346  return std::make_tuple(enable);
347  }
348 
349  auto asTuple()
350  {
351  return std::make_tuple(std::ref(enable));
352  }
353

356  EstimationControl cmd;

585  ALL = 0x7,
586  };

3601 struct InitializationConfiguration
3602 {
3603  struct AlignmentSelector : Bitfield<AlignmentSelector>
3604  {
3605  typedef uint8_t Type;
3606  enum _enumType : uint8_t
3607  {
3608  NONE = 0x00,
3609  DUAL_ANTENNA = 0x01,
3610  KINEMATIC = 0x02,
3611  MAGNETOMETER = 0x04,
3612  EXTERNAL = 0x08,
3613  ALL = 0x0F,
3614  };
3615  uint8_t value = NONE;
3616 
3617  AlignmentSelector() : value(NONE) {}
3618  AlignmentSelector(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
3619  operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
3620  AlignmentSelector& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
3621  AlignmentSelector& operator=(int val) { value = uint8_t(val); return *this; }
3622  AlignmentSelector& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
3623  AlignmentSelector& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
3624 
3625  bool dualAntenna() const { return (value & DUAL_ANTENNA) > 0; }
3626  void dualAntenna(bool val) { value &= ~DUAL_ANTENNA; if(val) value |= DUAL_ANTENNA; }
3627  bool kinematic() const { return (value & KINEMATIC) > 0; }
3628  void kinematic(bool val) { value &= ~KINEMATIC; if(val) value |= KINEMATIC; }
3629  bool magnetometer() const { return (value & MAGNETOMETER) > 0; }
3630  void magnetometer(bool val) { value &= ~MAGNETOMETER; if(val) value |= MAGNETOMETER; }
3631  bool external() const { return (value & EXTERNAL) > 0; }
3632  void external(bool val) { value &= ~EXTERNAL; if(val) value |= EXTERNAL; }
3633  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
3634  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
3635  };
3636  enum class InitialConditionSource : uint8_t
3637  {
